
Automatic coupon applier is a chrome extension which helps any noraml user to obtain or fetch that available coupon for a particular emmorce website which gives the most discount for a comodity.
This is an automatic coupon applier for all the online marketing and e commerce websites which are famous and have a valid coupon service. This chrome extension automatically finds and applies coupon codes when you shop onlinewith just a single click.

A very user friendly extension is easy to load and use. All you do is Load the extesnion package and install it.Thereafter, whenever you visit an e-commerce website and go to the checkout page of  a comodity, a small icon for obtaining the coupon code comes. Clicking it gives you the most discount oriented coupon available within a minute .

Techologies used for making this chorme extesnion are Javascript and basic html,css and xml.
